thread.title: Charles

author: Charles
title: Charles
text: Gift A was unable to arrive at the agreed time however he telephoned me and we rearranged a time suitable to him. He was concerned about finishing at the originally arranged time so he brought a fellow worker and the pair finished the task well within the previously agreed finish time. The work completed was good, and they cleaned up when finished. I would be happy to have him/them again
